  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dragon Expedition is a fantasy adventure game that tells the story of the Eastern world being controlled by an unidentified robot prophet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The girl unexpectedly becomes involved in this conspiracy and becomes a dragon slayer warrior, heading alone to the Western demon world to search for the Dragon Crystal and save her home. From then on, embark on the long journey of slaying demons and collecting dragon eggs. The game includes different scenes from the East and the West, with various monsters waiting for you to challenge. The unique gameplay of Royal Dragon Air Combat will bring you a different experience. Is it defeating the dragon to save our home? Or have they been conquered by evil forces? Only by embarking on a long journey and writing fate with a sword can we obtain the final answer!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1. Control the flying dragon for high-altitude combat and engage in an air-to-air confrontation with the evil dragon.                                                                                                         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras/d9ed9198432f893b3923ead1f3e1397f.poster.avif?t=1748767990\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras/d9ed9198432f893b3923ead1f3e1397f.webm?t=1748767990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras/d9ed9198432f893b3923ead1f3e1397f.mp4?t=1748767990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras/a201a7f0dbcd261a66adfcdff63f0ffd.avif?t=1748767990\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras_big/a201a7f0dbcd261a66adfcdff63f0ffd.avif?t=1748767990 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2. Multiple scenes to explore freely.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras/f87aeb2bca7038e342477ef37ce35f83.avif?t=1748767990\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras_big/f87aeb2bca7038e342477ef37ce35f83.avif?t=1748767990 width=800 height=498 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras/085edd4beabd6caa12842f185400dbaa.avif?t=1748767990\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras_big/085edd4beabd6caa12842f185400dbaa.avif?t=1748767990 width=800 height=450 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras/6fd40f0b2c7796647d2b4dd69f2bd354.avif?t=1748767990\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras_big/6fd40f0b2c7796647d2b4dd69f2bd354.avif?t=1748767990 width=800 height=448 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3. Multiple skills will lend you a helping hand.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras/b7355251cf779fc138ae885b15036230.avif?t=1748767990\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras_big/b7355251cf779fc138ae885b15036230.avif?t=1748767990 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4. Different bosses bring you different combat experiences.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras/6af15594f5a994d07f5a03c94e059641.avif?t=1748767990\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras_big/6af15594f5a994d07f5a03c94e059641.avif?t=1748767990 width=800 height=498 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras/d11bfcb6e4bba245368f057137890315.avif?t=1748767990\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras_big/d11bfcb6e4bba245368f057137890315.avif?t=1748767990 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >5.Whether the Eastern world can return to its golden age and prosperity lies in your sword.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras/07771cea1bc5cc3945b66201a4958472.avif?t=1748767990\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3435310/extras_big/07771cea1bc5cc3945b66201a4958472.avif?t=1748767990 width=800 height=448 /></span></p>",
